tedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:06:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a78bc243ee56b01c3bf0f50fa7b4a74d8fcfbb63","tid":5890,"uid":6213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:07:46.000Z","msg":"自己打飛機囉"},{"pid":"f2b3a6fc739579c15da88e27bb10703863f7a2e9","tid":5890,"uid":22136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:09:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同男朋友本身住得遠 <br />\n最近佢勁忙 忙到已經一兩個星期冇見<br />\n要去到下個月尾先見得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係住香港但好似long d咁<br />\n嗚呀好辛苦呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我地好少whatsapp<br />\n佢話唔慣message<br />\n所以要等夜晚FaceTime<br />\n想問下絲打們掛住男朋友果陣會做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實有facetime已經算係咁<br />\n利申：好憎facetime</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我同佢反而會facetime住做自己野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我同佢會傾今日做過啲咩<br />\n又會望下對方一陣 但咁樣好似更加掛住佢<br />\n勁想衝去搵佢 但我知佢真係好多野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9bbf85496379d042b038d7eae2c1699b2f16317","tid":5890,"uid":22136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:11:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同男朋友本身住得遠 <br />\n最近佢勁忙 忙到已經一兩個星期冇見<br />\n要去到下個月尾先見得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係住香港但好似long d咁<br />\n嗚呀好辛苦呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我地好少whatsapp<br />\n佢話唔慣message<br />\n所以要等夜晚FaceTime<br />\n想問下絲打們掛住男朋友果陣會做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你自己有冇啲咩愛好呀<br />\nTry to make yourself busy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有keep住自己搵節目<br />\n但一岀街見到街上情侶一對對係到放閃<br />\n就會諗起佢 其實好想自己唔諗起佢<br />\n但其如果我冇再諗起佢<br />\n係咪姐係等於我唔再在乎佢 愛佢"},{"pid":"7f4d4f75ca84652df9ec0e56bed0161fc07526bc","tid":5890,"uid":22136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:12:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同男朋友本身住得遠 <br />\n最近佢勁忙 忙到已經一兩個星期冇見<br />\n要去到下個月尾先見得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係住香港但好似long d咁<br />\n嗚呀好辛苦呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我地好少whatsapp<br />\n佢話唔慣message<br />\n所以要等夜晚FaceTime<br />\n想問下絲打們掛住男朋友果陣會做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實有facetime已經算係咁<br />\n利申：好憎facetime</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解憎嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實如果有得見 我都唔想FaceTime <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2757be61c2001cfa20ae0e2f618b865c79d8d7a9","tid":5890,"uid":28035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:15:44.000Z","msg":"做d咩忙到連小小時間都無呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0173970d92c2e19ab7894cf882a87bf6851f20d8","tid":5890,"uid":16243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:18:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"832eb14b0da1b3da1100bfb87af034c52122b207","tid":5890,"uid":22136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:22:20.000Z","