m就知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同埋千其唔好問<br />\n你係咪唔愛我呀冇咁中意我依啲問題<br />\n拍拖講信個信字<br />\n佢咁忙再聽到依啲問題應該會爆炸<br />\n等多排啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好啦唔該你呀絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽完你講好似安落啲"},{"pid":"fc201bec01046b36d31bb6124ea5b5004a7ad9c4","tid":5890,"uid":16243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:04:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f592a7b61601d5e4f351932b738f0b97f2e45882","tid":5890,"uid":22136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T08:49:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做d咩忙到連小小時間都無呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢有好多project 做完project又要開始溫exam <br />\n話要考曬exam 完sem先見得面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一兩個鐘食餐飯嘅時間都冇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想知但我唔敢問 怕佢覺得我煩<br />\n因為佢已經講左完sem先見<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4個月姐唔係好長啦<br />\n<br />\n反正都就完sem<br />\n佢忙極起碼有FaceTime 吖<br />\n可能你隔幾日問佢一齊食飯好冇<br />\n佢唔想嘅話就等啦 因為開得口話幾時先見<br />\n證明佢真係有原因唔想出<br />\n忙又好乜都好 完sem就知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同埋千其唔好問<br />\n你係咪唔愛我呀冇咁中意我依啲問題<br />\n拍拖講信個信字<br />\n佢咁忙再聽到依啲問題應該會爆炸<br />\n等多排啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好啦唔該你呀絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/